PN,46901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1773511563
OL,3,CPay-out given to Sainsbury's worker
OL,4,Cleft out of social media post
OL,6,FA Sainsbury's store manager who was
OL,7,Fleft off his boss's International
OL,8,FMen's Day social media post has been
OL,9,Fawarded #12,000.
OL,11,FDarren Cooper was on leave for anxiety
OL,12,Fwhen his regional director uploaded a
OL,13,Fpost celebrating the male leaders who
OL,14,F"all show up for work each day, put on
OL,15,Fa name badge and provide support,
OL,16,Fguidance and leadership".
OL,18,FWhen he saw he was not included, Mr
OL,19,FCooper was left feeling "excluded,
OL,20,Fhumiliated and violated", the
OL,21,Femployment tribunal in Cardiff heard.
OL,26,@vD@AOUxD@XO]{D@YOU|D@XO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,497,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1773511563
OL,3,CPay-out given to Sainsbury's worker
OL,4,Cleft out of social media post
OL,6,FThe tribunal ruled that he had been
OL,7,F"humiliated" by the post and he won
OL,8,Fhis claim for harassment related to
OL,9,Fdisability and unfavourable treatment
OL,10,Fbecause of something arising in
OL,11,Fconsequence of disability.
OL,13,FA later remedy hearing decided he will
OL,14,Freceive #11,852 in compensation,
OL,15,Fincluding #7,500 for injury to
OL,16,Ffeelings.
OL,18,FMr Cooper began working at Sainsbury's
OL,19,Fin 1993 and said he had "orange blood"
OL,20,F` a reference to the colour of the
OL,21,Fchain's branding ` the tribunal heard.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@LO]{D@YOU{D@fO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,497,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1773511563
OL,3,CPay-out given to Sainsbury's worker
OL,4,Cleft out of social media post
OL,6,FIn 2010, he became manager of the
OL,7,FPontypridd store in South Wales, the
OL,8,Ftribunal was told.
OL,10,FHe took sick leave due to anxiety in
OL,11,FJuly 2022.
OL,13,FIn November, his line manager Matt
OL,14,FHourihan posted on Yammer and LinkedIn
OL,15,Fto celebrate International Men's Day,
OL,16,Fit was heard.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,497,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1773511563
OL,3,CPay-out given to Sainsbury's worker
OL,4,Cleft out of social media post
OL,6,FMr Hourihan wrote: "I'd like to take a
OL,7,Fmoment to celebrate the male leaders
OL,8,Fin my team and say thank you for all
OL,9,Fthat you do to help make our stores
OL,10,Facross South Wales, Gloucestershire
OL,11,Fand Worcester places where colleagues
OL,12,Flove to work and customers love to
OL,13,Fshop.
OL,26,@nD@TOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,497,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1773511563
OL,3,CPay-out given to Sainsbury's worker
OL,4,Cleft out of social media post
OL,6,F"All of you do this whilst leading
OL,7,Fbusy lives outside of work too,
OL,8,Fdealing with health, family and
OL,9,Fpersonal issues in the same way that
OL,10,Feveryone else does, yet you all show
OL,11,Fup for work each day, put on a name
OL,12,Fbadge and provide support, guidance
OL,13,Fand leadership to the thousands of
OL,14,Fcolleagues that work on our region.
OL,16,F"Thank you & Happy International Men's
OL,17,FDay everyone! Matt
OL,18,F_internationalmensday2022 _sainsburys."
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOUzD@gO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/9
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
